<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-32-0299 </DOCNO><TEXT>A method of absorbed organ dose calculations for persons subjected toin vivo diagnostic radioisotope thyroid examinations carried out afterthe administration of NaI(/sup 131/I) is presented. The biokinetic datafor sodium iodide were taken from the literature. In the result the absorbedorgan doses and the effective dose equivalents for persons under examinationwere obtained as a function of thyroid condition. 10 refs., 4 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>